Package com.hotels.beans.generator.core

Class TransformerSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hotels.beans.generator.core.TransformerSpec
  • public class TransformerSpec
extends Object
    This class is used to build a Transformer implementation model to map between a source and destination types. The model is a TypeSpec object that can be further modified if needed, and serialized to source code.

      • build

        public <A,​B> com.squareup.javapoet.TypeSpec build​(Class<A> source,
                                                        Class<B> destination)
        Build a transformer model to map from a source to destination type. The generated model implements the Transformer interface and provides mapping code to instantiate a destination object and map values from the source object.
        Type Parameters:
        A - the source type
        B - the destination type
        Parameters:
        source - the source to read values from
        destination - the destination where to map values
        Returns:
        a transformer model
